commit message:
Errnous behavior when output contains $$ (in this case displaying

Issue: all of askinteger, asksign, csetup in ctensor, demo do not work.
Root cause: Loop in onEditorAction() handling nested qe() did not
consider intermittent user input as above.

requested. See Release plan 2.3 for more details.
